RECIPE to run PhotonAnalysisUtils under release 15.2.0
======================================================


* configure athena for release 15.2.0

* check out HEAD version of PhotonAnalysisUtils and compile:

	cmt co PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils
	cd PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/cmt
	make
	cd -

* check out specific tags of PhotonAnalysisAlgs and PhotonAnalysisTools 
  and build:

	cmt co -r PhotonAnalysisAlgs-00-01-07 Reconstruction/egamma/egammaAnalysis/PhotonAnalysisAlgs
	cmt co -r PhotonAnalysisTools-00-00-12 Reconstruction/egamma/egammaAnalysis/PhotonAnalysisTools
	cd Reconstruction/egamma/egammaAnalysis/PhotonAnalysisAlgs/cmt
	cmt broadcast cmt config
	cmt broadcast make
	cd -

* replace existing file PhotonCluster_jobOptions.py with a fixup in our share dir:

	cp PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/share/PhotonCluster_jobOptions.py.fixup InstallArea/jobOptions/PhotonAnalysisAlgs/PhotonCluster_jobOptions.py

* ... and be optimistic: Run! 

	mkdir run
	cp PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/share/*.py run
	cp PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/share/*.root run
	cp PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/share/*.txt run
	cp PhysicsAnalysis/StandardModelPhys/PhotonAnalysisUtils/share/*.dat run
	cd run
	ln -s <your-favourite-AOD> AOD.pool.root
	athena.py PAUanalysis_jobOptions.py

